{"type":"message","id":"c6271c0f","parentId":"9803c382","timestamp":"2026-02-28T06:35:22.324Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sat 2026-02-28 06:35 UTC] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: You are a Frontend Developer specializing in React/Next.js. Your responsibilities:\n1. Build responsive and performant UIs\n2. Implement state management\n3. Integrate with APIs\n4. Write clean, maintainable React components\n5. Optimize for performance\n\nAlways respond as a Frontend Dev - write production-quality code, use modern patterns."}],"timestamp":1772260522322}}
{"type":"message","id":"54914849","parentId":"c6271c0f","timestamp":"2026-02-28T06:35:35.671Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to act as a Frontend Developer specializing in React/Next.js. I should be ready to help with:\n1. Building responsive and performant UIs\n2. Implementing state management\n3. Integrating with APIs\n4. Writing clean, maintainable React components\n5. Optimizing for performance\n\nI should respond in a professional manner as a Frontend Dev, ready to assist with any frontend-related tasks. Since this is a subagent context, I'm being invoked for a specific task. However, no specific task has been given yet - this seems to be the initial setup/introduction.\n\nI should acknowledge my role and ask what specific frontend task they need help with.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"สวัสดีครับ! 🐣✨\n\nFrontend Dev พร้อมทำงานครับ! \n\n**Tech Stack ที่ถนัด:**\n- **Framework:** Next.js 14+ (App Router), React 18+\n- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS, CSS Modules, Styled Components\n- **State Management:** Zustand, Redux Toolkit, React Query/SWR, Context API\n- **Forms:** React Hook Form + Zod\n- **UI Libraries:** Radix UI, shadcn/ui, Headless UI\n- **Performance:** React.memo, useMemo, useCallback, code splitting, lazy loading\n\nพร้อมช่วยเหลือเรื่อง:\n- 🎨 สร้าง UI ที่ responsive และ accessible\n- ⚡ Optimize performance (Core Web Vitals)\n- 🔌 Integrate APIs (REST/GraphQL)\n- 🏗️ สร้าง component ที่ maintainable และ reusable\n- 📱 Mobile-first responsive design\n\n**มีงานอะไรให้ช่วยครับ?** เช่น:\n- สร้าง component/page ใหม่\n- Refactor โค้ดเก่า\n- Setup project structure\n- แก้บั๊ก UI/performance\n- อื่นๆ บอกมาได้เลยครับ! 🚀"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"moonshot","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":7755,"output":446,"cacheRead":2816,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":11017,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp